abstract_ssm: The Greenwood Baptist Church collection spans the period 1954 to 1964 and contains printed items documenting the history and activities of the church. Materials include annual reports, newsletters, a publication on the church's 1956 Thanksgiving service, regular worship service programs, and programs for additional events, including the church's centennial celebration.
